    <item>
      <title>尽管报复性关税，我们的大豆货物航行到中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/us-soybean-cargoes-sail-to-china-despite-retaliatory-tariff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据运输数据，我们的大豆中有30多个货物居住在中国，预计将在北京对美国农业商品的报复性关税下个月生效后，预计将近一半。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/us-soybean-cargoes-sail-to-china-despite-retaliatory-tariff</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 01:24:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
